38:12.563 --> 38:15.026
But this is not a law of bondage.

38:15.682 --> 38:20.292
When God calls us to obedience, He's not calling us into chains and bondage.

38:20.493 --> 38:25.223
He's calling us away from chains and bondage to freedom.

38:25.243 --> 38:27.207
God's commands are not a burden.

38:27.287 --> 38:29.412
